window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"When I say, therefore, that [my brother] has better powers of observation than I...I am speaking the exact and literal truth.\" (Sherlock Holmes) </p> <p>This story occurs when Mycroft, an athletic Cambridge graduate, assists the secretary of State. He becomes embroiled in a mystery in Trinidad based on actual history. </p> <p>Kareem Abdul-Jabbar is a huge Holmesian, seven-foot-two tall, basketball's all-time leading scorer, and a US cultural ambassador. Anna Waterhouse is a professional screenwriter and script consultant.</p>"; 
